Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:20.02,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\be1}挖掘出更强的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:25.97,OP_cn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\be1}Rise to my feet!
